about.summary: Pexpect makes Python a better tool for controlling other applications.

name: pexpect
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "4.2.0" %}

package:
  name: pexpect
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: pexpect-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/p/pexpect/pexpect-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  md5: 8071ec5df0f3d515daedafad672d1632

build:
  number: 1
  script: python setup.py install

requirements:
  build:
    - python
  run:
    - python
    - ptyprocess  # [not win]

test:
  imports:
    - pexpect

about:
  home: http://pexpect.sourceforge.net/
  license: ISC
  summary: Pexpect makes Python a better tool for controlling other applications.

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - jquast
    - pelson
    - takluyver
